R. O práise the Lórd, all you nátions.

16 He was mánifested in the flésh,
víndicated in the Spírit.

R. O práise the Lórd, all you nátions.

He was séen by ángels,
procláimed among the Géntiles.

R. O práise the Lórd, all you nátions.

He was belíeved in throughóut the wórld,
taken úp in glóry.

R. O práise the Lórd, all you nátions.
